
<div id="cssday" class="cjsf-day">
  <div id="about" class="banner">
    <div class="container-fluid">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-xs-12">

            <h1>Cascadia<span class="thin">CSS</span></h1>
            <p class="left lead"><%- description %></p>
            <img src="/assets/img/cssday/css-hex-icon-ver02.png" class="track-icon" />

        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="content">
    <%
    if(typeof schedule !== 'undefined') { %>
      <%- partial("../_partials/day/schedule", schedule) %>
    <% }
    %>

    <%
    if(typeof speakers !== 'undefined') { %>
      <%- partial("../_partials/day/speakers", speakers) %>
    <% }
    %>


    <div id="speaking" class="content">
      <div class="container-fluid">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-xs-12">
            <h3 id="speaking" class="text-center">Speaking / Call For Proposals</h3>
          </div>
          <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4 col-sm-push-8">
            <p class="text-center">
              <a class="btn btn-primary btn-lg speak-at" href="https://github.com/cascadiajs/2015.cascadiajs.com/blob/master/proposals/README.md">
                Speak at CascadiaCSS&nbsp;&nbsp;<i class="fa fa-microphone"></i>
              </a>
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="text-justify col-xs-12 col-sm-8 col-sm-pull-4">

            <p>CascadiaCSS is an exciting addition to CascadiaJS this year. We will spend a full day exploring the latest and greatest technologies and techniques related to building amazing user experiences for the web, very much in the spirit of CSSConf. Some topics we'd like to explore:
              <ul>
                <li>User experience design</li>
                <li>Advanced CSS</li>
                <li>Sass / LESS / Stylus / PostCSS</li>
                <li>Responsive design</li>
                <li>Cross-platform tips & tricks</li>
                <li>SVG</li>
                <li>Tooling</li>
                <li>Accessibility</li>
              </ul>
            </p>
            <p>We are running an open Call for Presenters and invite the CSS community to submit a talk. Diversity of voices is important to our community, so please don't think that you need to be a web celebrity in order to speak.</p>
            <p><strong class="blue">The deadline to submit a proposal is March 15, 2015 11:59pm UTC-1200</strong>. If it's still March 15th, no matter where you are in the world, you still have time!</p>
            <p>When youâ€™re ready to submit a proposal, read the <a href="https://github.com/cascadiajs/2015.cascadiajs.com/blob/master/proposals/README.md">instructions on GitHub</a> to get started. You are free to submit (and even revise) proposals up until the deadline. Our reviewers will be offering feedback for those ambitious enough to get their talks submitted earlier. Please help us spread the word!</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <%
    if(typeof sponsors !== 'undefined') { %>
      <%- partial("../_partials/day/sponsors", sponsors) %>
    <% }
    %>

    <%
    if(typeof staff !== 'undefined') { %>
      <%- partial("../_partials/day/staff", staff) %>
    <% }
    %>

  </div>
</div>